name: Beast Deity King Barbaros
desc: This card can attack all monsters your opponent controls, once each. You can Tribute monster(s) you control whose total Levels equal 8 or more; Special Summon this card from your hand. You can banish 1 "Barbaros" monster face-up from your field or from your GY, then target 2 cards your opponent controls; destroy them. You can only use each effect of "Beast Deity King Barbaros" once per turn.
